      <title>台湾反对派推动法律改革 加大召回难度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/taiwan-opposition-advance-legal-changes-that-make-recalls-harder</link>
      <description><![CDATA[台湾反对派立法者推动法律改革，使罢免民选官员和议员变得更加困难，这一有争议的举措将帮助他们获得立法多数席位，并以此对抗赖清德总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/taiwan-opposition-advance-legal-changes-that-make-recalls-harder</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 05:16:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
