      <title>卢拉称巴西唯一的问题就是高利率</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/lula-says-only-thing-wrong-with-brazil-is-high-interest-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴西总统路易斯·伊纳西奥·卢拉·达席尔瓦周日晚间在接受电视采访时表示，巴西的利率过高，日益严重的财政问题的责任在于央行的政策制定者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-16/lula-says-only-thing-wrong-with-brazil-is-high-interest-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 16 Dec 2024 02:04:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
